      • getMapTile

        public Drawable getMapTile(long pMapTileIndex)
        Description copied from class: MapTileProviderBase
        Attempts to get a Drawable that represents a MapTileIndex. If the tile is not immediately available this will return null and attempt to get the tile from known tile sources for subsequent future requests. Note that this may return a ReusableBitmapDrawable in which case you should follow proper handling procedures for using that Drawable or it may reused while you are working with it.
        Specified by:
        getMapTile in class MapTileProviderBase
        See Also:
